{"tid":1807453,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［民調］捉鬼撚一律當左膠處理","createTime":"2020-01-01T23:09:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T00:18:01.000Z","uid":191139,"like":47,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"87e114dcf272b86f750933493f9ccf7103db2375","tid":1807453,"uid":191139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T23:09:43.000Z","msg":"因為捉鬼情況險峻，捉到 你又打佢唔到，萬一捉嘅係同路人，好似元旦遊行咁，絕對百害而無一利<br />\n<br />\n為此，本人於連登做一次民調，如果比率高於4:1，捉鬼撚一律當左膠處理<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：捉鬼撚一律當左膠處理<br />\n負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：捉咪捉囉關你撚事"},{"pid":"1518d5823404e031d4bca92919e556ecc1c650da","tid":1807453,"uid":191139,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T23:10:55.000Z","msg":"如果 正評高過負評嘅ratio係4:1，請立即做文宣，停止捉鬼，否則一律當左膠處理"},{"pid":"3f061804aacf08903fe0379eee8d832dffba4b0a","tid":1807453,"uid":191139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T23:11:19.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"39dd2239ae563a47ea2f9ae2a651ac513864020d","tid":1807453,"uid":191139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T23:11:34.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"f127aea394780785369afda5c7ca1ea74f5d7f3d","tid":1807453,"uid":191139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T23:11:45.000Z","msg":"推推3/3"},{"pid":"a1745292b65f12243e943e476c05d8fc382609b0","tid":1807453,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T23:21:22.000Z","msg":"唔捉鬼啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"929a5e0f5a29de2ad2b8a2805e9b79857cee3b3a","tid":1807453,"uid":191139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T23:23:40.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"852c8650aaf4fd6cd82daa93602ed2983fb1c41a","tid":1807453,"uid":191139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T23:24:22.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"a109440dbb8aafc56a3c7216286d7c